{"_id":"hans00000001","name":"Hans Müller","type":"hero","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"archetype":"Idealist","nation":"eisen","background":"Soldier","traits":{"brawn":{"value":4},"finesse":{"value":2},"resolve":{"value":3},"panache":{"value":2},"wits":{"value":1}},"skills":{"investigation":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"stealth":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theft":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"legends":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sorcery":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theology":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"aim":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"athletics":{"value":3,"specialty":true},"melee":{"value":4,"specialty":true},"sailing":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"strategy":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"survival":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"intrigue":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"protocol":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"selfControl":{"value":1,"specialty":false},"engineering":{"value":1,"specialty":false},"humanities":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"science":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"empathy":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"persuasion":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"perform":{"value":0,"specialty":false}},"combatAptitudes":{"attack":{"trait":"brawn"},"defence":{"trait":"finesse"},"damage":{"trait":"brawn"},"toughness":{"trait":"resolve"},"manoeuvre":{"trait":"brawn"}},"wounds":{"minor":0,"dramatic":[false,false,false,false],"helpless":false},"heroPoints":1,"biography":"<p>Eisen bodyguard hired to protect Hugues. Learned a brutal lesson: death never warns you. Joined Los Vagabundos because the idea that one could kill 'to save souls' is unbearable to him.</p><p><strong>Advantages:</strong> Dracheneisen Panzerfaust, Idealist, Duelist Academy (Mauer aus Eisen), Perfect Balance, I Won't Die Here, Foolhardy, Passionate, Soldier</p>","notes":""},"items":[],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hugues0000001","name":"Hugues de la Chapelle Montmoront","type":"hero","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"archetype":"Schemer","nation":"montaigne","background":"Politician","traits":{"brawn":{"value":1},"finesse":{"value":2},"resolve":{"value":2},"panache":{"value":4},"wits":{"value":3}},"skills":{"investigation":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"stealth":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"theft":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"legends":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sorcery":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theology":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"aim":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"athletics":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"melee":{"value":1,"specialty":false},"sailing":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"strategy":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"survival":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"intrigue":{"value":4,"specialty":true},"protocol":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"selfControl":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"engineering":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"humanities":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"science":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"empathy":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"persuasion":{"value":4,"specialty":false},"perform":{"value":2,"specialty":false}},"combatAptitudes":{"attack":{"trait":"finesse"},"defence":{"trait":"panache"},"damage":{"trait":"wits"},"toughness":{"trait":"resolve"},"manoeuvre":{"trait":"panache"}},"wounds":{"minor":0,"dramatic":[false,false,false,false],"helpless":false},"heroPoints":1,"biography":"<p>Montaigne diplomat and Vagabundo. Smiles, bows, and quotes protocol, but knows the slightest misstep could spark a crisis. Joined Los Vagabundos to act for the greater good from inside the highest circles.</p><p><strong>Advantages:</strong> Reputation (Upright), Schemer, Staredown, Friend at Court, Indomitable Will, Intuitive, Politician, Relentless</p>","notes":""},"items":[],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
