{"_id":"manuela000001","name":"Manuela de Olivera de la Cruz","type":"hero","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"archetype":"Cursed Heir","nation":"castille","background":"Officer","traits":{"brawn":{"value":2},"finesse":{"value":2},"resolve":{"value":3},"panache":{"value":2},"wits":{"value":3}},"skills":{"investigation":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"stealth":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theft":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"legends":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sorcery":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theology":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"aim":{"value":2,"specialty":true},"athletics":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"melee":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"sailing":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"strategy":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"survival":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"intrigue":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"protocol":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"selfControl":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"engineering":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"humanities":{"value":1,"specialty":false},"science":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"empathy":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"persuasion":{"value":1,"specialty":false},"perform":{"value":0,"specialty":false}},"combatAptitudes":{"attack":{"trait":"finesse"},"defence":{"trait":"wits"},"damage":{"trait":"resolve"},"toughness":{"trait":"brawn"},"manoeuvre":{"trait":"resolve"}},"wounds":{"minor":0,"dramatic":[false,false,false,false],"helpless":false},"heroPoints":1,"biography":"<p>Castillian army officer and member of Los Vagabundos. Her father is a Villain allied with the worst scoundrels. She seeks to prove she is not doomed by blood to follow his path.</p><p><strong>Advantages:</strong> Firearms Specialist, Team Player, Cursed Heir, Leadership, Camaraderie, Altruistic, Officer, Unfortunate</p>","notes":""},"items":[],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"veronica00001","name":"Veronica Cardinale","type":"hero","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"archetype":"Conspirator","nation":"vodacce","background":"Sorte Strega","traits":{"brawn":{"value":2},"finesse":{"value":2},"resolve":{"value":2},"panache":{"value":3},"wits":{"value":3}},"skills":{"investigation":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"stealth":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"theft":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"legends":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sorcery":{"value":3,"specialty":true},"theology":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"aim":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"athletics":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"melee":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sailing":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"strategy":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"survival":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"intrigue":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"protocol":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"selfControl":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"engineering":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"humanities":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"science":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"empathy":{"value":4,"specialty":true},"persuasion":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"perform":{"value":0,"specialty":false}},"combatAptitudes":{"attack":{"trait":"panache"},"defence":{"trait":"wits"},"damage":{"trait":"panache"},"toughness":{"trait":"resolve"},"manoeuvre":{"trait":"panache"}},"wounds":{"minor":0,"dramatic":[false,false,false,false],"helpless":false},"heroPoints":1,"biography":"<p>Vodacce Sorte Strega and widow. Carefully smothered every sign of sorcery to avoid being promised to a prince-merchant. Joined Los Vagabundos because their cause spoke to her: striking the powerful by using their secrets as weapons.</p><p><strong>Advantages:</strong> Sorcery (Sorte Strega), Conspirator, Barterer, Extended Family, Oath, Curious, Illuminating, Sorte Strega (once per game Force Fate free)</p><p><em>Note: Add a Sorte Strega sorcery Item to this character to enable the sorcery tab.</em></p>","notes":""},"items":[],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
